<div class="item">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="hidden-xs testimonial-padding-wrapper">
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-img-wrapper hidden-xs">
              <div class="testimonial-img-inner-wrapper">
                <% url = "homepage/testimonies/Jehan-de-Castet_18.png" %>
                <%=  cl_image_tag url,
                  class: 'avatar-xl box-shadowed',
                  fetch_format: 'auto',
                  width: 250,
                  crop: 'scale' %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-txt-wrapper">
              <div class="visible-xs img-wrapper-mobile">
                <%=  cl_image_tag url,
                class: 'avatar-m box-shadowed',
                fetch_format: 'auto',
                width: 150,
                crop: 'scale' %>
              </div>
              
              <div class="testimonial-text-inner-wrapper">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="testimonial-title_">
                    Jehan de Castet
                    , 
                    Co-Fondateur et Président
                    @
                    <a href='http://www.fluo.com/' target='_blank' class="company-name">Fluo</a>
                     - 
                    France
                  </h3>
                  <p class="testimonial-quote">
                    "The Beeleev team introduced me to Geoffroy de Becdelievre,
                    Founder of MarcoVasco, which was Fluo’s first travel agency
                    client. Fluo has greatly benefited from MarcoVasco’s ability to integrate innovation which itself has seen its travel insurance sales increased by 100% in the meantime."
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
